        <updateDate>2021-10-06T18:31:47Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Keep Vaccines Voluntary Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires businesses, institutions of higher education, and state and local governments that receive certain COVID-19 relief funds to certify that they will not limit access to services or otherwise discriminate on the basis of an individual's COVID-19 vaccination status.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
